
SHUTDOWN(1)                                           SHUTDOWN(1)

NAME
       shutdown() - shuts down the mud

SYNOPSIS
       varargs void shutdown(int code)

DESCRIPTION
       The MudOS shutdown() efun has no security.  This SimulEfun
       overrides the MudOS shutdown() efun to provide security.

LOCATION
       /secure/SimulEfun/SimulEfun.c

SEE ALSO
       the shutdown() efun

Author
       Descartes of Borg

